        Return -1 if it doesn't exists.

        INPUT:

        - ``i`` - int - index of the state
        - ``j`` - int - index of the label

        OUTPUT:

        return a int, successor of the state i following edge j

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: from badic.cautomata import *
